_:N950e34b77ea84f988b978854dccd7dd5 <http://schema.org/description> "VisitEngland (VE) is the national tourist board for England, responsible for marketing England to domestic and established overseas markets and for improving England’s tourism product. VE is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
